### Lend Simulation

This endpoint allows you to simulate a lending scenario by providing the loan ID and the loan amount.

#### Request Body

- `loan_id` (number) - The ID of the loan.

- `amount` (number) - The amount of the loan.

- `principal_amount` (integer) - The principal amount for the loan simulation.

- `rate` (integer) - The rate of interest for the loan simulation.

- `loan_duration` (integer) - The duration of the loan in months.


#### Response

The response of this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "code": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "total_repays": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "weekly_installments": {
                    "type": "string"
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

This endpoint retrieves the proof picture associated with a specific loan ID. The response for this request is an image in JPG format.

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "loan_id": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "proof_picture": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "binary"
    }
  }
}

 ```

This endpoint retrieves a list of lenders for a specific loan based on the provided loan ID.

The response of the request can be documented as a JSON schema as follows:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "code": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "data": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "id": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "loan_id": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "user_id": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "amount": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "agreement_file_path": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "created_at": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "updated_at": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

### Loan Disbursement

This endpoint is used to disburse a loan.

#### Request Body

- `loan_id` (text) - The ID of the loan to be disbursed.

- `user_sign` (file) - The signature of the user.


#### Response

The response is in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "code": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

 ```
